OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and breezy across much of
OL,6,Fthe region, although some light rain
OL,7,Fpossible across the Pennines during
OL,8,Fthe morning. Plenty of sunny spells,
OL,9,Fespecially through the afternoon.
OL,10,FTemperatures around average.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FEvening sunshine followed by
OL,13,Fa mostly clear night. Cloud building
OL,14,Fin the north during the early morning
OL,15,Fmay bring a spot of rain. Remaining
OL,16,Fbreezy along coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
