OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCloudy through the morning on
OL,6,FFriday, some sunny spells through the
OL,7,Fafternoon. Cloudier again into the
OL,8,Fevening with the possibility of some
OL,9,Frain.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fand breezy for much of the period with
OL,13,Fspells of rain at times, mostly
OL,14,Faffecting western hills with drier
OL,15,Fconditions further east. Temperatures
OL,16,Faround average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
